  "introHtml": "As a <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>software developer</span>, I enjoy building <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>practical, user-centered applications</span>. My career has introduced me to <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>cloud infrastructure</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>REST APIs</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>automation</span>, and <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>front-end performance</span>, and I <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>strive</span> to provide the <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>best experience</span> for <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>customers</span> and <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>users</span>. I enjoy tackling <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>complex problems</span> and breaking them down into <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>logical blocks</span>, in order to <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>deliver</span> a <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>cohesive experience</span> to help people <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>achieve their goals</span>. <br><br> I'm also a <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>proud father</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>avid gamer</span> (top 3: <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>Kerbal Space Program</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>Factorio</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>Terraria</span>), and enjoy activities such as <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>skiing</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>longboarding</span>, and <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>flying</span> built-from-scratch <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>R/C airplanes</span>.",
